        "other_details": {
          "en": {
            "provenance": "translation_service",
            "value": "Participated in student movements since the age of 15, striving to raise and resolve educational issues of common students. Participated in the ten-year People's War, was arrested in 2057 BS and spent one and a half years in prison. Broke out of jail in 2058 BS and rejoined the People's War. Actively involved in relief, rescue, and reconstruction efforts for families affected by the devastating flood of 2071 BS and the earthquake of 2072 BS."
          },
          "ne": {
            "provenance": "imported",
            "value": "१५ वर्षको उमेरदेखि विद्यार्थी आन्दोलनमा सहभागी भई आम विद्यार्थीका शैक्षिक मुद्दा उठाएर समाधान गर्न प्रयत्न गरेको। दश वर्षीय महान जनयुद्धमा सहभागी भई काम गर्दा २०५७ सालमा गिरफ्तार भई डेढ वर्ष जेल जीवन बिताएको । २०५८ मा जेल ब्रेक गरी पुनः जनयुद्धमा सहभागी भईयो। २०७१ सालको विनासकारी बाढी तथा २०७२ को भूकम्पमा परी पीडित परिवारको राहत उद्दार तथा पुनः निर्माणमा सक्रिय ।"
          }
        },
        "qualification": {
          "en": {
            "provenance": "translation_service",
            "value": "Postgraduate"
          },
          "ne": {
